OL,13,     Gtheir bank card.
OL,14,G1115FHomes Under the Hammer
OL,15,     GWe head to the Kent coast to
OL,16,     Grevisit a renovation that's taken
OL,17,     Gsome time to finish. Jacqui
OL,18,     Gchecks out a large terrace as
OL,19,     Gwell as a tiny flat in a tale of
OL,20,     Gtwo contrasting projects.
